::DevilDuer::

DevilDuer swears, falling backwards and tripping over a table. By the time he 
gets to his feet, Diamond was gone.

"Slag! Computer, total clampdown, track that bot!!"

Looking at the console to see where Diamond had gone, DevilDuer sees that 
she's in the vents. He jumps up, sounds of the outside exits shutting as he 
jumps to the vent, clambering into it. Realizing he was stalking a 
possibly-poisonous snake, he jumps back down, activating his comm.

"Hey, everyone," he says into it, "There's a snake-bot on the loose. If ya 
see her, get her in stasis lock or somethin', I'll be there t' pick 'er up."

He runs out of the room, looking at his scanners, hoping that every exit was 
secured.
